messages.message: I missed the eng all hands due to a training session with paychex. where can I see the slides? as i understood it wasn’t recorded. it would be great if next time it could be announced in advance that a session will not be recorded so people can plan around it.

Hey @Felicia — Slides from Eng All Hands here. (https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1oU7350Od7JTA389yspSmYmLgmx8uxfbYlCutpfHytsc/edit#slide=id.gd404fcad0f_1_368) We did not record it as we wanted to allow for a more open discussion on pulse survey results. If you weren’t able to attend, please reach out to your manager who will be able to share insights from the meeting.
